Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.78,0:00:08.77,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,後鳥羽院著，出自『新古今和歌集』。）\N{\an8}（ほのぼのと春こそ空にきにけらし天のかぐ山霞たなびく
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.13,0:00:12.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又要迎来樱花的季节了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.10,0:00:17.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年又送走了一批前途无量的年轻人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.04,0:00:22.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是多么令人欣慰的一件事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.34,0:00:28.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后又将会有一批新的学子进入这所学校的大门
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.71,0:00:34.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将这些充满希望的年轻人们健全地培养起来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.29,0:00:38.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是我的使命  是我人生最大的幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.35,0:00:41.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您找我吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.58,0:00:43.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  请进
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.35,0:00:46.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问…？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.37,0:00:51.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉野屋老师  能告诉我  你最喜欢的词汇是什么吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.24,0:00:53.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最喜欢的词汇吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.62,0:00:56.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  我想年纪尚轻的吉野屋老师的话
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.39,0:01:02.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定会有什么能让年轻人们产生共鸣的座右铭
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.30,0:01:02.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,年轻！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.40,0:01:05.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该就是爱了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.36,0:01:09.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对于艺术的爱  以及对学生们的爱
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.74,0:01:12.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为可爱的学生们制作物品
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.39,0:01:14.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教他们画画的乐趣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.15,0:01:18.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对我来说  这就是爱了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.39,0:01:21.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有  对我自己的爱
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.44,0:01:22.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱真的超棒的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.60,0:01:25.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是超～级～棒的！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.10,0:01:28.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我已经很清楚了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.50,0:01:31.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前半段就拿来让我参考一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.39,0:03:26.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由乃亲  早安
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.06,0:03:27.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小宫  早安
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.20,0:03:29.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是大晴天真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.06,0:03:32.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  要出去购物呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.21,0:03:35.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小宫有做好准备了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.52,0:03:38.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没呢  现在才开始准备
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.27,0:03:40.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能让她们高兴就好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.57,0:03:42.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她们俩肯定都会吓一跳的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.01,0:03:44.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.59,0:04:04.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.60,0:04:05.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃莉同学
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.08,0:04:06.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是荠吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.28,0:04:11.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？有什么事吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.99,0:04:15.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…学姐们送来了份信件
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.64,0:04:16.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信件？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.34,0:04:20.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给小荠&乃莉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.87,0:04:24.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天傍晚5点来一下由乃的房间
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.41,0:04:26.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要空着肚子来哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.51,0:04:28.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,By 学姐们
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.98,0:04:29.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在几点了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.70,0:04:32.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,4点40分
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.62,0:04:35.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你  我做一下准备
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.19,0:04:37.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能稍微等我一会儿吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.03,0:04:38.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.71,0:04:43.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有称呼  叫乃莉就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.13,0:04:46.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  乃莉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.38,0:04:48.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…同学
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.42,0:04:49.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都说不用加了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.38,0:04:52.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.23,0:05:04.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底有什么事呢？明明就住在同一所公寓的说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.71,0:05:05.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.90,0:05:09.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,午安
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.07,0:05:10.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.00,0:05:12.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.82,0:05:18.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,#——·*@%￥*(!#$%
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.86,0:05:22.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…偷吃了草莓是我不好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.04,0:05:24.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这么回事…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.32,0:05:32.82,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（欢迎一年级生）
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.55,0:05:32.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎来到暖阳庄
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.92,0:05:34.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干杯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.84,0:05:40.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来  沙英学姐  先请你做一下暖阳庄的解说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.55,0:05:43.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是去年和我们说的那些
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.31,0:05:46.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.28,0:05:47.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暖阳庄
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.65,0:05:51.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是座落于山吹高中正对面的一所小公寓
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.76,0:05:54.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为聚集着美术科的怪人们而小有名气
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.37,0:05:57.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过那些人都已经毕业了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.74,0:05:59.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在住这里的只是些普通人而已
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.14,0:06:03.14,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（原201室）
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.30,0:06:06.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来  一年级的学妹们  敞开胃口大吃一顿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.20,0:06:08.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛  一副了不起的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.09,0:06:11.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,草莓的数量会变少  是拜谁所赐来着？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.23,0:06:17.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.97,0:06:20.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是自己做的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.12,0:06:22.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  是大家一起做的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.60,0:06:25.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特意为了我们做这种事  真是抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.58,0:06:26.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.99,0:06:29.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宫子不也帮忙一起做了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.36,0:06:32.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个学姐们刚搬来的时候也有举办吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.42,0:06:34.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎会吗？有办过
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.15,0:06:37.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那去年是怎样的？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.84,0:06:40.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小宫说送来了一封挑战书什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.65,0:06:44.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给由乃&宫子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.66,0:06:47.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天傍晚5点来一下寻的房间
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.04,0:06:49.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不许迟到&早到
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.85,0:06:51.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,By 沙英&寻
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.08,0:06:55.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为文章太有气势  所以误以为是挑战书了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.75,0:06:58.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.49,0:07:00.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们刚来时也有举办欢迎会的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.70,0:07:03.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉这已经成为每年的惯例了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.51,0:07:06.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好开心  谢谢大家
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.69,0:07:08.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么现在就…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.14,0:07:09.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,锵锵锵锵～
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.30,0:07:12.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宫子特制  Talk骰子登场
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.34,0:07:15.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如实回答骰到的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.69,0:07:17.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宫子  先来示范
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.13,0:07:19.26,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（喜欢吃汉堡吗？）
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.26,0:07:19.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.50,0:07:21.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那算什么问题啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.16,0:07:26.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那先从一年级生开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.65,0:07:28.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先来？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.92,0:07:30.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请吧  请吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.47,0:07:32.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.90,0:07:36.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中奖了  恭喜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.61,0:07:40.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.57,0:07:40.32,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（中奖）
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.44,0:07:45.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能同时享受甜和辣  真是奢侈
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.31,0:07:47.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说小宫
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.02,0:07:49.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给  下一位是乃莉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.40,0:07:51.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.48,0:07:54.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.74,0:07:55.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兴趣吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.68,0:07:56.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.95,0:07:59.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近的话  果然要算PC方面的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.32,0:08:01.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,CG和HTML之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.81,0:08:02.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有Flash
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.05,0:08:06.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为没什么钱  所以只能到处找免费软件下载
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.21,0:08:08.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.24,0:08:10.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没钱…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.81,0:08:17.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  我来之前这里是没连网线的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.01,0:08:20.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听不懂你说的话  真是抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.26,0:08:22.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要多谢文明开化的风潮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.30,0:08:25.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但有点失望的是  连的不是光纤
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.30,0:08:28.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还以为肯定是光纤的说  网速慢死了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.52,0:08:30.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回声号？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.52,0:08:33.33,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（因为乃莉说速度慢，由乃就误把“光纤”当成了“新干线号”了。\n这两个词日文发音相同，所以才会联想到站站停的低速列车“回声号”。）
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.02,0:08:36.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  接下来就由乃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.73,0:08:38.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  我骰
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.22,0:08:42.47,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（让荠向学姐们提问！！）
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.52,0:08:41.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是要让我提问吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.63,0:08:42.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.64,0:08:44.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…那就…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.16,0:08:47.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学姐们为什么会学画画呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.03,0:08:49.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说到为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.04,0:08:51.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很有深度的问题呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.82,0:08:54.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先从扔骰子的由乃开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.10,0:08:57.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会学画画…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.05,0:09:00.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么…为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.60,0:09:01.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.19,0:09:05.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由乃
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.30,0:09:08.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有没有什么其它的问题了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.34,0:09:11.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  那个…那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.84,0:09:13.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学校开心吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.93,0:09:16.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  学校很开心的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.52,0:09:17.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上的课很有意思
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.06,0:09:19.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,校风也很沉稳
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.00,0:09:21.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有很有趣的老师
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.04,0:09:24.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总是穿着奇怪的服装
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.18,0:09:26.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胸部超大  还有脱衣癖
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.95,0:09:29.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.10,0:09:33.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经9点了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.06,0:09:36.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多该结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.66,0:09:38.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天是入学仪式吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.27,0:09:39.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.34,0:09:42.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多谢款待  很好吃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.15,0:09:45.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  放在那儿就行的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.13,0:09:48.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…由乃学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.59,0:09:50.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能再问你一个问题吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.31,0:09:55.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个人住
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.60,0:09:58.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会寂寞吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.52,0:10:01.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会  完全不会
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.00,0:10:06.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢大家  晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.89,0:10:08.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢大家
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.65,0:10:09.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.52,0:10:14.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉气氛弄得有点紧张呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.10,0:10:15.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.80,0:10:19.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉没能好好对上话呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.78,0:10:23.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系的  以后相处的时间多得是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.63,0:10:25.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯嗯  那么…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.03,0:10:26.95,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（现在才能说得出口的事）
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.15,0:10:29.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始第二轮吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.18,0:10:31.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就我们几个吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.86,0:10:36.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经这个时间了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.12,0:10:39.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡过头了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.96,0:10:41.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为睡得晚了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.26,0:10:43.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.56,0:10:48.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小时候就算晚睡  早上也能按时起床的说
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.96,0:10:52.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不敢相信自己那时还跑去做广播体操
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.51,0:10:56.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安  肚子饿了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.48,0:10:59.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小宫  早安
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.45,0:11:01.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要去做广播体操吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.96,0:11:03.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子会更饿的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.17,0:11:09.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.70,0:11:11.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学姐  学姐  特大新闻
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.38,0:11:13.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  这怎么行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.10,0:11:16.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不赶快去参加入学仪式的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.36,0:11:19.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是  我是刚刚回来的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.99,0:11:20.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.69,0:11:22.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寻
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.75,0:11:24.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说怎么了？出什么事了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.86,0:11:26.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  荠
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.19,0:11:36.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,普通科！？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.83,0:11:44.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就住在这附近
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.24,0:11:47.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为觉得离家近一点比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.22,0:11:49.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就参加了山吹高中的普通科入学考试
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.48,0:11:50.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果考中了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.09,0:11:54.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后父亲就突然被调到外地去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.46,0:11:58.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原以为父亲是独自去外地工作
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.24,0:12:01.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但爸爸完全不会做家务
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.04,0:12:04.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈就跟着去了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.26,0:12:08.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是…什么都不会做的说
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.15,0:12:10.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会做料理
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.23,0:12:12.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扫卫生也笨手笨脚的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.12,0:12:14.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,画画也不好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.67,0:12:16.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也没什么特长和兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.83,0:12:19.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一点都不像呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.49,0:12:26.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  在消沉些什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.31,0:12:29.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,荠也是有优点的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.98,0:12:32.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃…乃莉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.10,0:12:35.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我还不是很了解
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.24,0:12:38.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说得太直白了啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.27,0:12:44.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到那孩子是普通科的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.98,0:12:49.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难怪会问为什么会学画画呢  原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.00,0:12:52.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么大家之前都没注意到呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.96,0:12:54.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为谁都没有问过吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.15,0:12:55.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.48,0:12:59.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还以为住进这里的全都是美术科的学生
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.48,0:13:03.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是稀奇呢  这是暖阳庄的首例吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.22,0:13:07.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过突然让她独自生活  真的不要紧吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.69,0:13:10.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原本打算住自己家里的  是吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.21,0:13:14.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,问过事情原委后  总觉得她有点可怜呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.62,0:13:17.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系的  肯定马上就能习惯的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.89,0:13:18.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能那样就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.11,0:13:24.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚刚忘记问荠的发型是在哪做的了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.29,0:13:25.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个编的发环吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.74,0:13:27.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  浏海也剪得很可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.34,0:13:30.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她说她住在附近的  会不会是车站前的那家？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.33,0:13:32.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是“olive”？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.24,0:13:36.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“olive”！好怀念啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.28,0:13:38.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前一次和小宫去“olive”  是什么时候的事啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.70,0:13:41.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是去吃烤肉的那天  所以就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.29,0:13:43.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去年夏天
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.81,0:13:46.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,4月6日～4月7日  ‘完’  待续
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.77,0:13:51.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,7月19日  ‘olive’
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.29,0:14:12.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小宫
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.37,0:14:17.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小宫  发生什么事了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.45,0:14:18.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.66,0:14:20.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思  没事…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.88,0:14:24.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用灶台烤肉  结果就烧起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.99,0:14:28.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肉都烤焦了…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.71,0:14:33.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,头发都烧焦了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.22,0:14:36.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没烧伤已是万幸了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.71,0:14:38.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说  小宫
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.94,0:14:40.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不要一起去美容院
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.32,0:14:43.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也正想去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.07,0:14:46.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美容院吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.27,0:14:50.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近一直是让我老哥帮我剪的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.50,0:14:53.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你哥哥是美容师吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.67,0:14:55.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是哦  是园艺师
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.07,0:14:57.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然是修树的！？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.83,0:15:01.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,值得推荐的美容院？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.06,0:15:04.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,车站前的“olive”就不错呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.79,0:15:06.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“olive”吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.45,0:15:08.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和沙英也一直是去那里的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.83,0:15:09.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微等一下哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.19,0:15:14.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我记得应该有些能够半价的优惠券
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.97,0:15:16.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是帮大忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.79,0:15:24.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  真是抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.72,0:15:26.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再稍微等等
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.87,0:15:28.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.88,0:15:32.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寻学姐  那些全部都是积分卡吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.11,0:15:32.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,俨然是一位主妇啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.83,0:15:34.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.95,0:15:36.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给你～
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.69,0:15:39.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.05,0:15:40.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感谢之至
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.98,0:15:48.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是家可爱的店呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.65,0:15:49.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真干净啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.11,0:15:59.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.36,0:16:11.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真凉快
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.74,0:16:13.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.51,0:16:15.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,双胞胎美容师很少见吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.90,0:16:17.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真抱歉让你们受惊了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.90,0:16:19.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没那回事  很漂亮的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.95,0:16:21.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,店也装饰得很可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.01,0:16:25.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“橄榄色”这店名也很妙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.93,0:16:29.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实店名是按我们的名字起的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.14,0:16:31.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按名字？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.84,0:16:32.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.26,0:16:35.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OLI…VE？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.60,0:16:36.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,VE？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.49,0:16:40.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的姓叫做折部
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.07,0:16:44.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.83,0:16:45.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有的事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.90,0:16:47.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个就帮您取下了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.03,0:16:48.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.89,0:16:52.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就仅仅修剪一下吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.56,0:16:53.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要剪成什么样的呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.95,0:16:54.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.33,0:16:58.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修得整洁一点就行  不用剪掉太多
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.89,0:17:02.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请帮我修得有女人味一些
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.38,0:17:04.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很困难的要求啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.67,0:17:07.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您希望我怎么弄？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.33,0:17:08.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.82,0:17:11.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请把我弄得像京美人一样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.95,0:17:13.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这要我如何是好…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.17,0:17:18.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来就为您洗发并做护理
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.88,0:17:19.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.90,0:17:25.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  是水温太高了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.05,0:17:28.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是  只是有点痒而已
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.55,0:17:29.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧  小宫…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.70,0:17:36.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问  这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.13,0:17:40.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得  可能是太痒了的缘故
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.96,0:17:45.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就开始剪罗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.91,0:17:47.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.09,0:17:50.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先把椅子升高点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.08,0:17:52.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也稍稍升高点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.03,0:17:55.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真开心
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.57,0:17:58.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也好久没有披着围布了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.04,0:18:00.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像是晴天娃娃一样～
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.91,0:18:12.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用剪刀修剪的手艺真是高超呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.15,0:18:15.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感谢您的赞美之词
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.80,0:18:17.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后面的头发稍微打薄一点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.67,0:18:18.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.33,0:18:21.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您也要修薄一点吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.85,0:18:22.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.25,0:18:24.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平时也会修薄吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.95,0:18:26.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  一直都会
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.35,0:18:28.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会修到什么程度呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.76,0:18:29.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相当薄
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.92,0:18:31.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修到扁扁平平的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.94,0:18:33.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扁扁平平…？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.25,0:18:37.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来为您吹干
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.17,0:18:39.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果太热了请跟我说
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.96,0:18:40.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.39,0:19:02.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小宫
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.27,0:19:04.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发…发生什么事了？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.60,0:19:08.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得发质变好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.27,0:19:12.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用了护发素  做了护理之类的就变得柔顺了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.60,0:19:14.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,买下吧  小宫
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.08,0:19:15.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然就可惜了一头秀发了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.73,0:19:19.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.59,0:19:21.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.82,0:19:25.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由乃
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.61,0:19:26.23,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}（亲）
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.26,0:19:27.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等着你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.95,0:19:31.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夕阳的余光照进来了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.22,0:19:34.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真抱歉  需要放下百叶窗吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.67,0:19:36.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用  没关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.94,0:19:38.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.40,0:19:40.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剪成这样您感觉如何呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.68,0:19:45.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  非常感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.43,0:19:48.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么也请看一下后面吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.23,0:19:49.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.29,0:20:10.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.30,0:20:11.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敬请下次光临
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.20,0:20:26.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小宫
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.45,0:20:27.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变了个人似的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.69,0:20:29.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么弄的？去做过缩毛矫正了？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.16,0:20:31.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是哦  只做了护理
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.95,0:20:33.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真漂亮呢  柔柔顺顺的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.86,0:20:37.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我下次是不是也去拉个直发试试呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.21,0:20:41.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定也有很多人羡慕寻学姐松松软软的头发呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.65,0:20:44.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但小宫变得很有女人味了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.05,0:20:48.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但不出三天应该就会变回原状了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.20,0:20:50.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我说
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.22,0:20:54.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也变得有女人味了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.88,0:21:01.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这房里充满了美容院的气味呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.69,0:21:02.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.01,0:21:06.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  美容院特有的香香的气味呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.25,0:21:10.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是该去理个发了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.05,0:21:12.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微有点长了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.42,0:21:16.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就由我来帮你理吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.31,0:21:18.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得现在能够做到呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.01,0:21:21.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要这样啦  不是自己的头发就这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.02,0:21:24.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么就由我来…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.01,0:21:25.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就连由乃也…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.02,0:21:50.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天不洗头也不要紧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.09,0:21:57.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美容院的气味…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.68,0:22:04.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也稍微变得有点女人味了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.65,0:22:06.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.99,0:22:09.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,7月19日  ‘完’  待续
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.10,0:23:43.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一年级生们都已经熟悉山吹高中了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.46,0:23:44.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没  还差得远呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.00,0:23:47.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也还有很多不了解的地方呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.41,0:23:49.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山吹高中的七大不可思议
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.36,0:23:51.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实有活动的教室存在呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.97,0:23:54.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,传说中会有新生消失的那个？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.51,0:23:55.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.75,0:23:57.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然不可能是真的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.05,0:23:58.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一话是
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.66,0:24:01.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‘4月8日～9日  决断’
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.37,0:24:04.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,‘12月10日  因为杯子太小了’
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.72,0:24:06.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们在山吹高中里等着你
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.67,0:24:08.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要来看哟
